ğŸ”¹ PART 2 â€” GITHUB AUTO-START (YAML, WHAT YOU WANT)
This is where the â€œG6 G7 WROOOOMâ€ happens ğŸ˜„
GitHub Actions is the correct, compliant way.
âœ… What this CAN do (legit):
Run on a schedule (2026, daily, weekly, hourly)
Pull public RSS feeds
